<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Stands do not carry fire regularly in California. <i>Rhododendron columbianum </i>sprouts when disturbed; <i>R. groenlandicum </i>is widely known in Canada as a post-fire sprouter (Gucker 2006b).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
